Insider Activity


Individual




Daniel H. Schulman



Mr. Daniel H. Schulman is President & Chief Executive Officer at PayPal, Inc., Chairman at Symantec Corp., a Member at Lead Director Network, and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at PayPal Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Xoom Corp., Flextronics Corp., Rutgers University (New Jersey), Autism Speaks, Inc., and PayPal Holdings, Inc.
Mr. Schulman was previously employed as Group President-Enterprise Group by American Express Co., Independent Director by The Telx Group, Inc., President-Prepaid Group by Sprint Nextel Corp., Independent Director by Flextronics International Ltd., Chief Executive Officer & Director by Virgin Mobile USA, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Priceline.com, Inc., President by AT&T WorldNet, an Advisor by Greycroft LLC, and President-Consumer Markets Division by AT&T Corp. He also served on the board at Net2Phone, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Middlebury College and an MBA from The Leonard N Stern School of Business.



